  "title": "supervisor",
  "description": "<p>The Responsibilities:</p><p>Provide the general day-to-day technical functions and duties</p><p>Arrange/coordinate appointments and bookings for meetings and company car use</p><p>technical and backup support to executives and other staff for the whole company</p><p>Monitor contracts, contract expiry, and prepare quotes</p><p>Backend support for special projects and events</p><p>Any other ad-hoc duties assigned</p><p>job highlights 4 off days monthly, rest days depend on schedule. able to work long hours and late in evenings and weekends</p><p>Competitive salary 3k and above</p><p>Positive and nurturing working environment</p><p>Work location: co office area duration: permanent</p><p>Requirements</p><p>qualifications - diploma or high school diploma</p><p></p><p>Work experience- at least one year working experience in related fields</p><p>job type- full time</p><p>Required languages: English and able to communicate with mandarin speaking customers</p><p>If you have an interest in applying for this role, please WhatsApp me at 98198786 to apply. Only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Priority will be given to Singaporeans</p><p></p><p>Young hon Lim/ manager</p><p>Render private limited</p><p>EA licence no 15c7827</p><p>EA reg no R1550906</p>",
